Was there ever such a Devil?— 'gad she frighted me— for this pretty Instrument had certainly bin sheath'd in my Guts if I had opos'd her longer— well I'll straight to Fieske, discover our adventures, and beg his pardon— and hereafter agree with him. 

That amongst all Mischifs that with Vice ingage; 

Nothing so Barbrous as a Strumpets Rage. Exit.
